    "opening": "Let me show you what this looks like in real-time. Watch the data flow.",
    "narration": "[As animation plays] On the left, data is generated at your sources—100 events per second. It flows into Expanso. [Pause] Watch what happens: Expanso filters 70 events per second—that's the noise, the debug logs, the duplicate data you don't need. It transforms the remaining data—masking PII, enriching fields. It routes intelligently to the right destinations. [Pause] On the right, only 30 events per second reach your platforms. Same insights. 70% less cost.",
